# Dependency lockfile — uv generates this on `uv sync`. Phase 0 installs via
# `pip install '.[dev]'` per .github/workflows/ci.yml; we have NOT yet decided
# to adopt a committed uv.lock for reproducibility. Remove this entry only as
# a deliberate dependency-management decision, not as a side effect of running
# uv locally.
